Anhinga - Spirits Of The Canyon 320v0 (Big Papi) Native American Music Flute Guitar



review at Amazon:

We picked up this CD while on vacation at Knott's Berry Farm in LA. It is very cool! It was on sale in the Mystery Lodge gift shop which is a neat America Indian exhibit/show. Very relaxing/spiritual instrumental music with lots of pan flute. Guaranteed to be one of your all time favorites!
